tip.text: Fresh prawns made into butter prawns ❤️ Enjoyed the sotong celup tepung & siput bamboo asam pedas 👍🏼 Ikan pari bakar so-so. But tomyam was a disappointment, arrived cold & not sour/spicy at all 😭
Waiters were all very friendly when I was here. The natural mussels were good but I would avoid the curry sauce next time. Lobster soup's too salty for us tho :(
The waffle tastes good as compared to the one we tried at a random stall. €4.50 for waffle with whipped cream & dark chocolate sauce 😊
Really love the waffles here - buttery, light and airy texture , the way we like it. Perfect when paired with vanilla bean ice cream & whipped cream ❤️
Nasi lemak biasa is RM9, add a tiny bowl of sotong sambal, it becomes RM17 😓 And if you're going to charge a crazy price, at least don't make people curse at your food 😒
